summary: Device CA certificate API testing
description: |
    Tests the device CA certificate management API covering:
    - Uploading device CA certificates to rendezvous server
    - Listing registered certificates
    - Retrieving certificates by fingerprint
    - Deleting certificates
    - API validation and error handling

test: ../../rpm/test-device-ca-api.sh

framework: shell

duration: 30m

tag:
  - fdo
  - api
  - device-ca
  - certificate
  - rpm
